text: Khalifa Ababacar Diouf is a retired judoka from Senegal. Diouf competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics, the 1992 Summer Olympics, and the 1996 Summer Olympics. He was born on 24 March 1958.Khalifa Diouf == References == Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Senegalese judoka Category:Olympians for Senegal
